section.city-section
  .wrapper
    .city-section__container
      img.steps-section__img(src="images/cloud-red.svg" loading="lazy" width="680" height="223" alt="image")
      h2.city-section__title.font-w-a-regular.font-s-50
        | Начните 
        br.no-br
        | свой бизнес 
        br.no-br
        | прямо сейчас
      .city-section__sub-title.font-w-i-regular.font-s-18
        | Проверьте, свободен ли ваш город 
        br
        | для работы по франшизе
      form.city-section__form(data-feedback-form)
        input.input.city-item(type="text" name="city" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Город")
        input.input.city-item(type="tel" name="phone" autocomplete="off" data-inputmask="'mask': '+7 (999) 999 9999'" placeholder="Телефон")
        button.btn.city-item(type="submit") Проверить
      img.city-section__img(src="images/city-section-img.jpg" loading="lazy" width="1120" height="960" alt="image")
